{"tid":1595864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳浩天被控非法集結及襲警","createTime":"2019-09-26T09:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T09:31:42.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"600ad5ae2c802e377a8c371ac9a9157384e160f3","tid":1595864,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190926/large/1569485039_29db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190926%2Flarge%2F1569485039_29db.jpg&h=6c422280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨前召集人陳浩天在個人facebook專頁表示，今午向警方報到後，被警方正式起訴非法集結及襲警，案件將於明日在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天於上月29日晚在香港國際機場準備出境時，未能成功過關，隨後被警員拘捕，據悉涉及一宗有組織罪案及三合會調查科（O記）的案件。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190926/large/1569484887_42db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190926%2Flarge%2F1569484887_42db.jpg&h=a828797f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52572e9204c45bd426edf0d976e2e343d8f27a27","tid":1595864,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"10.1 前又開始拉大台 , 黃之峰應該都走唔甩"},{"pid":"8969c1c056952e8eb0689c7c9f8d33d0816f2422","tid":1595864,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"堡主又比人拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cbee4dae817f634c0923af049f13e929e43d92","tid":1595864,"uid":266207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8969c1c056952e8eb0689c7c9f8d33d0816f2422","tid":1595864,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"堡主又比人拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔係拉提堂啫<br />\n你話堡主襲警，打死都無人信啦"},{"pid":"cdf6b7d168b57b524aa0b634258e8bf9d8f12946","tid